<text id="02-output-contract" title="Python Code Quality — Output Contract" version="1.0.0" est_tokens="900" depth="essential">
  <summary>Output schema for the subagent applying python-code-quality. Encodes required boolean checks against the artefact under review.</summary>

  <section title="Schema (JSON Schema fragment)">
    <code lang="json"><![CDATA[
{
  "$schema": "https://json-schema.org/draft/2020-12/schema",
  "type": "object",
  "required": ['ruff_configured', 'mypy_strict', 'coverage_gate>0', 'precommit_installed', 'no_legacy_black_isort'],
  "properties": {
    "ruff_configured": { "type": "boolean" },
    "mypy_strict": { "type": "boolean" },
    "coverage_gate>0": { "type": "boolean" },
    "precommit_installed": { "type": "boolean" },
    "no_legacy_black_isort": { "type": "boolean" }
  },
  "additionalProperties": false
}
]]></code>
  </section>

  <section title="Required fields">
    <list>
      <item>ruff_configured</item>
      <item>mypy_strict</item>
      <item>coverage_gate&gt;0</item>
      <item>precommit_installed</item>
      <item>no_legacy_black_isort</item>
    </list>
  </section>

  <section title="Valid example">
    <example type="good">
      <code lang="json"><![CDATA[
{
  "ruff_configured": true,
  "mypy_strict": true,
  "coverage_gate>0": true,
  "precommit_installed": true,
  "no_legacy_black_isort": true
}
]]></code>
      <note>All gates green; methodology applied.</note>
    </example>
  </section>

  <section title="Invalid example">
    <example type="bad">
      <code lang="json"><![CDATA[
{
  "ruff_configured": false,
  "mypy_strict": false,
  "coverage_gate>0": false,
  "precommit_installed": false,
  "no_legacy_black_isort": false
}
]]></code>
      <note>All gates red; methodology not applied — fix the violations before claiming completion.</note>
    </example>
  </section>

  <section title="Self-check checklist">
    <list>
      <item>Every required field is present and boolean true.</item>
      <item>Artefact references the rule id from 01-core-rules.xml (e.g., r1-ruff-single-tool).</item>
      <item>No extra properties outside the schema.</item>
    </list>
  </section>
</text>
